title: 3 and Out - Week 2 NFL Reaction
itunes:title: 3 and Out - Week 2 NFL Reaction
description:
John reacts to Week 2 NFL action, including what he saw in the Packers SNF win over the Bears, if the Saints can win with Dennis Allen and Jameis Winston, if the Niners are better without Trey Lance, Kyler Murray’s video game-like performance in the OT thriller in Vegas, and if Tua should be the the Dolphins franchise QB going forward.
